  Complete STPA analysis includes:
  1. Safety constraint definition
  2. Control structure modeling  
  3. Unsafe Control Action identification
  4. Causal scenario analysis
  5. Safety requirement generation
  """
  def execute_stpa_analysis do
    IO.puts """
    🔬 STAMP STPA ANALYSIS: CONTAINER OPERATIONS
    ==========================================
    
    Analysis Date: #{DateTime.utc_now() |> DateTime.to_string()}
