    **Current**: Stop development on warnings/errors
    **STPA Enhancement**: Stop on safety constraint violations
    **Implementation**: Safety constraint violations trigger immediate halt
    **Agent Impact**: Safety issues get same priority as quality issues
    
    #### 5-Level RCA Enhancement
    **Current**: Root cause analysis for compilation/quality issues
